===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# [[late]]; near the end of a period of time
#* {{zh-x|及 年歲 之 未 晏 兮，時 亦 猶 其 未央。||ref=Chuci}}
# [[late]] in the [[day]]
#: {{zh-x|晏起|to get up '''late'''}}
#: {{zh-x|晏晝|[[afternoon]]|C}}
#: {{zh-x|放工 嗰時 好 塞{sak1}車，搞到 好 晏 先 返 到{dou3-2} 屋企{kei2}。|The traffic was quite bad when I left work, so I got home really '''late'''.|C}}
#: {{zh-x|天氣 報告 講 今朝 晏歇 會 落雨 末。|The weather forecast said it'll rain '''later''' today.|tr=sh:1thi chi5&6yu kau5&5kaon&1cin tsau1&5e shiq7+6we+8loq+6yu&0meq|SH}}
#: {{quote-book|nan-tws|year=Late Qing/Early Republic|title=zh:《蘇六娘金釵羅帕記》|location=潮州<t:Chaozhou>|publisher=李萬利|volume=3|page=11v|pageurl=https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/Page:CADAL13030386_古板新造蘇六娘金釵羅帕記全歌（卷一至卷三）.djvu/81}}
#:: {{zh-q|做乜 障 晏 未 走起|It is so '''late''', why has [he] not yet gotten up?|MN-T|tr=zo3 mih4 ziên3 uan3 bhuê7 zao2 ki2}}
# {{lb|zh|Cantonese}} [[lunch]] {{zh-mw|c:餐}}
#: {{zh-x|食晏|to have '''lunch'''|C}}
# [[sunny]] and [[cloudless]]
# [[peaceful]]; [[tranquil]]; [[serene]]
#: {{zh-x|河清.海晏|the (Yellow) River is clear and the sea is '''calm'''; the world is peaceful and prosperous}}
# {{surname|zh}}
#: {{zh-co|^晏 ^殊|{{w|Yan Shu|'''Yan''' Shu}} (Song dynasty poet)}}

